- EGL is not implemented.
- Floating-point GL entry points are not part of this Common-Lite build.
- Desktop OpenGL immediate mode, display lists, selection/name stack,
  polygon mode, quads, polygons, feedback, accumulation, evaluators,
  raster-position APIs, and color-index APIs are not public API.
- Mipmapping parameters are accepted, but the renderer uses level 0 only.
- Compressed texture and extension texture upload paths are unsupported and
  report GL errors.
- Depth testing remains tied to the existing TinyGL rasterizer behavior:
  triangle fills use the zbuffer path, and explicit depth-test toggling is
  mainly meaningful for lines.
- Verification is currently Nspire-build coverage plus manual device testing.
- Only the core APIs are supported; no extensions.
